beta_1 = 0.1911 [mS/uF]
    in [mS/uF]
beta_2 = 0.000349 [mS/uF] * exp(-1.062 * membrane.vfrt)
    in [mS/uF]
beta_ItoC2 = beta_2 * beta_i * alpha_C2ToI / (alpha_2 * alpha_i)
